Reqs

Create endpoints:
  - Create a new user
  - Create a new article
  - Edit an article
  - Delete an article
  - Return all articles (from all users) that contains the given tag(s) (1 or more)
  - Authentication with token

Models:
  User
  Article

Acceptance criteria
  - Github Public Repository
  - Express.js
  - Mongo DB
  - NTH: TDD

Stages
  - Project initialization
    - Nodemon/Babel               20m
    - Express                     15m
    - dotenv                      15m
    - Docker                      15m
    - MongoDB (docker-compose)    30m
    - Tests (Mocha/Chai)          15m
  - Auth                          30m
  - User creation                 1h
  - Article ABM                   3h